  "value": "^#CC8A4D;Archetype: Duellist^reset;\nThe Duelist is a melee-focused fighter that excels at opening with hyper-precise criticals from their unconventional ancient weaponry, before getting in close with melee and parrying. Duellists specialize well against bosses and elites, and their specialized weapons are extremely ammo-efficient.\n                                                ^cyan;But where are my claws? My claws were better.^reset;\n^#CC8A4D;Species: Neki^reset;\nAllegedly, \"Neki\" is merely a shorthand for the maneki-neko, a feline-human hailing from Gensyoko. They had once been known for their ability to bring fortune to markets; they still retain their agility and senses.\n                                                                   ^cyan;Oh, I love playing purretend! =^.^= ^reset;\n^#CC8A4D;Indomitable [Ability]^reset; - Taking more than 15 DMG grants +100% DMG RES for the next 3s | 30s Cooldown.\n\n^#CC8A4D;Flowing Water [Ability]^reset; - Successful parries heal the player for 4HP/s for 2s.\n\n^#CC8A4D;Blessed Shots [Ability]^reset; - Guaranteed crits on the next shot with a Bow, Crossbow, Throwing Weapon, or Muzzle-Loader | 10s cooldown.\n\n^red;Short-Sighted [Penalty]^reset; - -15% Proficiency with firearms. Does not apply for Bows, Crossbows, Throwing Weapons, or Muzzle-Loaders.\n\n^orange;Alcohol Addiction^reset; - ^cyan;Yuck, no thanks. You won't be getting that.  =>.<=^reset;"
